Entries.default: "You sure you're supposed to be down here?"
"See Captain Vilami if you have any business."
"The hours are lousy, but the job pays well."
"Better get topside. Ezzali will want a report."
"What a mess, hey? At least we made it through this feud in one piece."
"Atello didn't stand much of a chance against you."
"So, just to be clear... If Atello Valera turns up, we DON'T kill him?"
"Think we'll get paid the same, now that we don't have to worry about the Valeras?"
"Shame about Baer... That was you, right?"
